  "notes": [
    "This configuration resolves City of Tolleson zoning by intersecting runtime coordinates with Layer 52 of the public TOLLESON_PUBLIC feature service.",
    "The dataset is published for the City of Tolleson through AZGeo, Arizona's state geospatial clearinghouse, and permits anonymous public queries.",
    "TYPE is the published zoning code. COMMONNAME, document fields, source jurisdiction, and last-edited date are retained when populated because they may identify supplemental zoning information.",
    "The query is restricted to JURISDICTION = 'TOLLESON' because the layer also includes zoning polygons administered by Phoenix, Maricopa County, ADOT, the Roosevelt Irrigation District, and railroad interests within the broader planning area.",
    "District descriptions are normalized from the legend of the official City of Tolleson zoning map prepared September 9, 2025.",
    "The configured commercial fixture at Tolleson Plaza, 9550 W Van Buren Street, resolves to CORE, CORE District.",
    "The official map states that it is intended for reference purposes only and that aerial imagery may not match field conditions.",
    "A resolved zoning result supports permit research but does not replace review of applicable PAD documents, zoning cases, ordinances, stipulations, overlays, or confirmation by the City of Tolleson."
  ]
